author: Lidia Kelly
title: Australia demands coronavirus enquiry, adding to pressure on China
description: Australia on Sunday added to growing pressure on China over its handling of the novel coronavirus, questioning its transparency and demanding an international investigation into the origins of the virus and how it spread.
content:
